    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes Open Shortest Path First - Traffic Engineering (OSPF-TE) routing protocol extensions to support GMPLS control of Optical Transport Networks (OTNs) specified in ITU-T Recommendation G.709 as published in 2012.  It extends mechanisms defined in RFC 4203.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
